findings.title: Division before multiplication
findings.description: Multiple instances of division done before multiplication without proper method, potentially causing overflow/underflow.

findings.title: Redundant and uncallable function payBackETH()
findings.description: The payBackETH() function in the CarbonSlotAMMPancake contract is declared internal and not called inside any other function which makes the function redundant and uncallable.

findings.title: Typecasting msg.sender
findings.description: No need to typecast msg.sender, you can use transfer on it directly.
